Class PagedList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.v3.PagedList<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the element type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.Collection<E>, java.util.List<E>
    public abstract class PagedList<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.List<E>
    Defines a list response from a paging operation. The pages are lazy initialized when an instance of this class is iterated.
